law.text:
		The Council shall have the following responsibilities:

To foster the exchange of information between the federal, state, and local government;


To enhance Virginia's participation in the United States Environmental Protection Agency's Region III Response Team;


To review and evaluate the response to emergency situations and recommend changes to the Commonwealth of Virginia's Oil and Hazardous Materials Emergency Response Plan;


To provide ongoing analysis of the most recent technical developments for the remediation of discharges; and


To coordinate its activities with the Secure and Resilient Commonwealth Panel.
